Rating: 4
If you follow the recipe exactly, it makes a fantastically flavourful soup that does not need the additional spices and sugars that other reviews have suggested. Fresh ground pepper and a healthy spoonful of crème fraîche is all the accompaniment this soup needs. The only variation I ever make is skipping the water and adding extra white wine; this soup also freezes and reheats wonderfully.

